# utils/icons.py
#
# INLINE SVG ICON LIBRARY — SELF-CONTAINED, ZERO NETWORK
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# All icons are pure inline SVG — no CDN, no font, no network dependency.
# Renders perfectly in Playwright PDF (just <svg> markup).
#
# THREE-TIER SYSTEM:
#   Tier 1 — Generic stroke icons:  server, alert, chart, arrow…  (55 icons)
#   Tier 2 — Brand fill icons:      kubernetes, docker, kafka…    (40+ brands)
#   Tier 3 — Letter badge fallback: any unknown brand → styled letter badge
#
# DYNAMIC ICON RESOLUTION for new topics:
#   When the LLM requests [[icon:mongodb:64:#4EA94B]] and "mongodb" isn't in
#   Tier 1 or Tier 2, Python generates a clean letter badge:
#     → green circle with white "M" — still looks professional
